I'm the Game Technologies
Evangelist at Apple.

00:04:02.566 --> 00:04:05.576 A:middle
And, as Geoff said, I'm here
to talk to you about some

00:04:05.576 --> 00:04:09.086 A:middle
of the things we see in some
of the best games on iOS.

00:04:10.106 --> 00:04:11.996 A:middle
Now, there's a lot
of things that go

00:04:11.996 --> 00:04:13.706 A:middle
into making a great game.

00:04:13.946 --> 00:04:17.136 A:middle
And a lot of different ways to
describe that process, right?

00:04:17.136 --> 00:04:19.956 A:middle
But to echo back to what he was
