Is that they're just,
they're in a loop

00:37:52.466 --> 00:37:55.966 A:middle
where they're binding a texture,
drawing a quad, and then repeat.

00:37:55.966 --> 00:37:57.506 A:middle
Bind; draw; bind;
draw; bind; draw.

00:37:57.506 --> 00:38:01.656 A:middle
