00:38:15.276 --> 00:38:19.166 A:middle
So, you know, the theory behind
this becomes very important

00:38:19.246 --> 00:38:20.746 A:middle
to optimize this.

00:38:21.006 --> 00:38:24.356 A:middle
It's super important that
those developers find a way

00:38:24.356 --> 00:38:28.036 A:middle
to amortize that overhead
over more triangles.

